        <div class="mb-1">
            <span>The background tasks are managed with the help of <a href="https://www.hangfire.io/" target="_blank">Hangfire</a>.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-1">
            <span>The behind-the-scenes matrix operations are handled using <a href="https://numerics.mathdotnet.com/" target="_blank">MathNET Numerics</a>.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-1">
            <span>The download of data in is made possible also using <a href="https://github.com/OfficeDev/Open-XML-SDK" target="_blank">Open XML</a>.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-1">
            <span>The e-mail sending service is provided by <a href="https://sendgrid.com/" target="_blank">SendGrid</a>.</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
